transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Good evening sir, kaise hain?
Customer: Thik thak ji, bataiye ji.
Executive: Kaisi chal rahi hai services abhi?
Customer: Service ke upar kya karein jab koi humein sunata nahi hai toh phir hum kya kyun aapko pareshan karein.
Executive: Sir koi baat nahi, hamara toh farz hai na services ke regarding toh aapse bilkul puchenge kaisi chal rahi hai, kuch issues toh nahi hai. Dekho sir woh wali situation mein aapko bhi pata hai ki mere hath mein kuch nahi hai. Jitna mein koshish kar sakti thi maine aapke liye efforts kare but uss cheez mein mein kuch kar nahi pa rahi hu actually.
Customer: Dekhiye woh toh dekhiye uske upar jo bhi hote hain toh woh maan ke chaliye jo nau sikhiya hote hain wohi mujhe chhedte hain.
Executive: Hmm.
Customer: Baaki, baaki jitne bhi hote hain toh maan ke chaliye jo aaj rate lega woh 6 mahine baad aayega. Toh woh bhi pata hai woh WhatsApp ke upar hi. Abhi jaise ki ek, teen chaar client hain jo pichle 6 mahine se mere se price model sara kuch le chuke hain. Ab unke hath mein order hai. Woh direct mujhe call nahi kar rahe. Ya phir direct mujhe koi inquiry nahi dal rahe. Woh wapas se meri side pe IndiaMART pe hi dhund rahe hain. Aur jaise hi mein usko click karta hu ki yeh janaab kya dhundne aaye hain. Toh woh pata lagta hai ki unko maine 2 saal pehle price diya tha aaj ki date mein order unka confirm hai aur unhe material chahiye. Ab woh material India mein hai hi nahi available. Woh kahan se ho jayega?
Executive: Accha, toh sir woh directly aapke paas kyun nahi aa rahe?
Customer: Kyunki woh itne shatir hote hain na mam ki apna phone bhi woh format kar lete hain. Toh meri detail unke paas kahan se niklegi? Aur, aur jaise hi mera number unke paas jata hai waise woh pehchan jate hain ki Mishra ji bol raha hu mein.
Executive: Samajh gayi.
Customer: Toh woh sare mahir log baag hain, mahir logo ki abhi maan ke chaliye March tak toh yahi khel chalna hai. Isme IndiaMART ko kya hum dosh dein kya na dein kyunki woh 6 mahine hote hain running ke April ke baad October tak jisme ki woh log baag jitne aate hain woh nau sikhiya aate hain jisko maal nahi chahiye woh rate pata karne aayega. Koi project kharid kar aayega phir rate pata karne aayega. Ab toh STQC lag chuka hai ab toh rate pata karne wale zyada aate nahi hai ab toh kehte hain sir jo rate hoga aap de hi do.
Executive: Nahi dekho sir mera toh matlab main aapse puchhne ka sirf reason yeh hai ki services mein toh koi issue nahi aa raha kyunki simple si cheez hai ki dekhiye jo aapka location wala issue hai usme bahut baar hum try kar chuke hain but kyunki woh garment side pe hi woh wahan ka hai toh ab hum uska toh kuch nahi kar sakte but services mein aapko jo bhi help chahiye woh mein aapki definitely kar sakti hu bas isliye maine aapko call kiya ki abhi services mein.
Customer: Woh dekhiye woh toh dekhiye woh toh kuch nahi ho sakta uske liye mein bhi kuch nahi keh sakta ab kuch hone wala agar hota toh ho gaya hota. Toh woh toh chapter hi ab close hai. Ab toh reh gayi baat ki bhai service hai, service hai toh chalo ji abhi koi maramari nahi hai koi mera sar nahi phod raha toh mujhe, mujhe koi uske andar koi aisa hai nahi. Reh gayi baat leadon ka toh leadon ke andar bhi hai ki lead agar mein zyada consume karu tab bhi koi benefit na hai, na karu tab, tab uske andar bhi benefit hai. Na karne pe bhi benefit hai aur agar mein karta hu toh usme bhi koi benefit nahi hai bekar ka mobile ka sar dard apne dimag ka sar dard din bhar lage rahe aur aana wana kuch nahi hai toh isse badhiya hai ki loading kam karke dekho. Ab ho kya raha hai ki jitne project wale pad rahe hain woh rate lekar ke aaram se so jate hain. Koi mahina, dedh mahina, dedh mahina, do mahina is hisab se jagta hai jagne ke baad agar usne safely kyunki sare log ek jaise nahi hai market mein.
Executive: Sahi baat hai.
Customer: Toh market mein woh acche log hain unhone number save kar rakha hai unka jab order final hota hai toh woh batate hain woh pata laga ji mahine bhar toh IndiaMART pe kuch nahi aaya woh WhatsApp pe aaya toh woh WhatsApp pe jo aaya toh woh kahan se aaya woh bhi toh IndiaMART ke hi khate mein se aaya na. Toh woh beshak, woh beshak is saal ke khate mein se nahi aaya woh pichle saal ke khate mein se aaya. Toh wohi hisab kitab hai ki bhai jab maan ke chaliye ki ab isme pagal karne wale bhi log bahut sare aate hain woh at a time ab kal ek client tha jo ki raat mein phone karke baat kar rahe the 10 baje raat mein kahi call lagbhag call aayi hai mere paas 10 baje raat mein keh rahe hain sir mujhe CP plus ka yeh 2MP camera de do. Thik hai ji.
Customer: Ab mein raat ke 10 baje CP plus ko thodi na khol ke bataunga ki bhai available hai ya nahi hai.
Executive: Sahi baat hai.
Customer: Toh, toh maine bola sir subah aap, subah mein confirm karta hu subah se mein use 5 dafa confirm kar chuka hu ek dafa bhi usne jawab nahi diya ki haan ji chahiye ya nahi chahiye raat mein toh woh account mein account number bhi le liya usne payment karne ke liye bhi keh raha hai sir payment kar du abhi. Toh bhai 10 baje raat mein payment leke kya karunga subah tumhara account dhundunga ki tumhari payment kaise wapas karu.
Executive: Sahi baat hai.
Customer: Toh ek se badhkar ek dhurandhar hai mam market mein abhi sare shant hain.
Executive: Mein wohi bol rahi hu India mein aapko har tarah ka insan milta hi hai.
Customer: Woh dekhiye online baithe hain toh proper online baithe hain toh isliye pata hai ki bhai har tarah se kis tarah ke log aate hain ab ek hai Jammu Kashmir ke aaj woh IndiaMART pe lead dikha rahe the toh maine khola toh mujhe dikha ab woh Jammu Kashmir se Sanjay Sharma hai woh pichle 3 saalon se mujhse rate hi le rahe hain. Accha project, project bahut badhiya badhiya pakadte hain woh unki chahat kya hai ki unhe mein GEM pe registration de du. Ab GEM pe registration dene ka matlab hai ki aap agar mujhse 5 lakh, 10 lakh ka maal lete ho mein willing karta hu toh company ko keh sakta hu ki sir yeh mera supplier hai isko GEM pe registration de do. Aapne 500 rupaye ka maal nahi liya GEM pe company kaun register karke degi?
Executive: Sahi baat hai.
Customer: Toh unki headache hi kuch alag hai unki chahat hi kuch alag hai woh IndiaMART pe dhundte hain ki koi naya murga fase woh naya murga ke paas toh jate nahi hai woh purane murge ke paas hi chale aate hain.
Executive: Koi dikkat nahi hai baaki aapko services mein jab bhi kahin pe bhi meri help ki zarurat ho toh please mujhe call kariyega.
Customer: Thik hai.
Executive: Thik hai mam dekhiye woh toh jab agar koi mujhe sunata hai na kahin pe toh mein woh zyada der udhari rakhta nahi hu mein sochta hu ki mujhe is line ne sunaya hai mein is line ko bata toh du kam se kam ki yeh sunne ko mil raha hai.
Executive: Sahi baat hai.
Executive: Nahi nahi woh koi dikkat nahi hai aapne sunaya humne suna but aapko services mein koi bhi madad chahiye ho toh bejhijhak call kar dijiyega.
Customer: Thik hai mam.
Executive: Thik hai, thank you.
Customer: Thank you mam.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer expresses concerns about lead quality.

- Frustration with clients seeking rates only.

- Issues with location-based services.



Resolution:

- Executive acknowledged the customer's concerns.

- Executive assured assistance with services.

- Executive explained limitations with location issue.



Next Steps: 

- None



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Angry -> Neutral



@@@Key Topics:

- buyleads, services, location issue, gem registration
